title: Indians look to move forward versus S. Cameron
text: Indians look to move forward versus S. Cameron By KEVIN BRUCHHAUS Daily News Staff Writer ELTON – After suffering a 22-18 heart-wrenching defeat at the hands of the East Beauregard Trojans last Friday night, the Elton Indians (EHS) will look to get back on the good foot with a trip to Creole to take on the South Cameron Tarpons in a battle for third place in district 4-1A.  //www.jenningsdailynews.net/?p=34391   22
